Key Match Events: Malik Monk scored 26 points, had 12 assists, and four steals for the Kings
Domantas Sabonis recorded 22 points, 13 rebounds, and 7 assists for the Kings

Miscellaneous Highlights: The Kings dominated the Warriors to get the easy 129-99 win
